high_descs: Turn right and face the green can in front of you.
Take the soap from the green can in front of you.
Turn left then face the sink on your right.
Place the soap in the sink in front of you.
Turn right then face the toilet on your left.
Take the soap from the toilet in front of you.
Turn left then face the sink on your right.
Place the soap in the sink in front of you.
Turn right and walk to the green trash can that is sitting on the floor between the sink and the toilet
Pick up the bar of soap that is sitting in the trash can
Take a step to the left and face the sink
Place the soap in the sink
Take a step to the sink and stand in front of the green trash can that is sitting on the floor between the sink and the toilet
Pick up the bar of soap that is sitting on the back of the toilet
Take a step to the left and stand in front of the sink
Place the bar of soap in the sink to the right of the soap that is already in the sink
anns.task_desc: Place bars of soap in a sink

high_descs: Turn right and go to the trash can
Grab the bar of soap out of the trash can
Turn left and go to the sink
Put the soap in the sink
Turn right and go to the toilet
Grab the bar of soap off the top of the toilet
Turn left and go to the sink
Put the soap in the sink
anns.task_desc: Putting two bars of soap in the sink
